# Quiz Sampler — Phase 6 question types

This short notebook demonstrates the four quiz question types supported
by test mode. Toggle **📝 Test** in the header, start or load a progress
file, and try each one.

```text
?? [mcq] What is 2 + 2?
- 3
- [x] 4
- 5

?? [truefalse] Merge sort is stable.
>> [true] Equal keys keep their original order because merging is left-biased.

?? [numeric tol=0.01] What is g on Earth, in m/s²?
>> 9.81

?? Why does the vertical velocity of a projectile reach zero at the peak?
>> Because gravity has exactly consumed the upward component over the
ascent; an instant later the ball accelerates downward.
```

