## Quiz

?? [mcq] What is the time complexity of binary search on a sorted array of length *n*?
- O(n)
- [x] O(log n)
- O(n log n)
- O(1)
>> Each step halves the search space, giving a logarithmic number of steps.

?? [truefalse] Merge sort is a stable sorting algorithm.
>> [true] When merging, the implementation takes from the left half first on ties, preserving the original order of equal keys.

?? [numeric tol=0.01] What is the acceleration due to gravity on Earth's surface, in m/s²?
>> 9.81

?? Why does the vertical velocity of a projectile launched upward at angle θ reach zero at the peak of its trajectory?
>> Gravity decelerates the upward motion. At the peak, the initial upward component v·sin(θ) has been exactly consumed by −g·t; an instant later, the ball starts accelerating downward.
